  var transferPanel='<section class="notice danger assignment-transfer-panel"><strong>Different renter or vehicle transfer</strong><div>Use this only when the names are different people. Choose the current renter and every name/reference that also belongs to that renter. Every unchecked identity on this exact car moves to history, its WheelsonAuto autopay stops, and any mistaken cross-renter name link is revoked. Legacy Clover recurring still needs provider-side verification.</div><div class="field"><label>Current renter to keep</label><select id="assignmentTransferCurrent">'+transferOptions+'</select></div><div class="field"><label>Names or references that belong to the current renter</label><div id="assignmentTransferKeepList" class="assignment-transfer-keep-list">'+keepOptions+'</div><small>The selected current renter is always kept. Check another name only when it is truly the same person.</small></div><div class="field"><label>Transfer note</label><textarea id="assignmentTransferReason" placeholder="Example: Ashley is the new renter; Felicia is the previous renter"></textarea></div><label class="native-confirm"><input id="assignmentTransferConfirmed" type="checkbox"> I verified the checked names belong to the current renter and every unchecked vehicle assignment must end.</label><button class="btn danger" data-action="save-assignment-transfer" data-id="'+esc(vehicle.id||'')+'" '+(names.length<2?'disabled':'')+'>Keep current renter and end old assignment</button></section>';
